CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper June 2, 1945, pg. 13, reads: "AKA Graduates From Pitt - This quintette of beauty and cleverness is the net result of the Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority's members of Iota Chapter who were graduated Monday from the University of Pittsburgh. The lovely grads include: Jayne Bailey (seated), Emma Rose, Christine Smith, LaRue Jacobs and Shirley Washington (standing). - Courier Photo by Harris."
TitMainTitle: University of Pittsburgh graduates and Alpha Kappa Alpha sorority members Emma Rose, Christine Smith, LaRue Jacobs, and Shirley Washington standing behind Jayne Bailey seated in front, in interior with floral curtains and oriental rug
